            <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-primary); margin: 0.5rem 0; font-weight: 500;">"Whāia te iti kahurangi"</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin: 0.5rem 0;">"Seek the treasure you value most dearly"</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="house-values" style="background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: 0;">🏛️ Connection to Mangakōtukutuku College Values</h3>
