                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">
                    <strong style="color: var(--color-accent); text-transform: capitalize;">Whaimana:</strong> Integrity - Standing firm in truth and principle
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0.75rem 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                    This learning connects to the value of <strong>whaimana</strong> by encouraging students to [engage with content in ways that embody this value].
